{"tid":132613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【囚衣相】特首入獄：曾蔭權轉倉赤柱　繼續鐵窗生涯","createTime":"2017-02-24T03:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T06:07:14.000Z","uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f873b5386a2dbdd857a4122b6268a7f1e157aba6","tid":132613,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/photo/bkn-20170224100659023-0224_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170224110332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170224100659023-0224_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170224110332&h=4e83f569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特首入獄：曾蔭權轉倉赤柱　繼續鐵窗生涯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被裁定一項公職人員行為失當罪名成立，判監20個月的前特首曾蔭權爵士，連續兩晚在荔枝角收押所度過後，今早約10時45分由囚車移送赤柱監獄繼續鐵窗生涯。曾蔭權戴口罩及身穿囚衣，由懲教署人員押上囚車。<br />\n<br />\n曾蔭權在赤柱監獄服刑期間，預期會被安排囚禁於俗稱「水飯房」、每間面積僅約80平方呎的獨立囚室，日夜與鐵欄及三面牆相對。年屆72歲的曾蔭權預料最快明天開始需在囚房「打工」，一般相信「摺信封」將成為其主要工作之一。"},{"pid":"7be668a604a326d7f89236509915912deb9ac7ed","tid":132613,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"太平紳士巡視, 高級監督巡視, 有無投訴"},{"pid":"3a62b7305c6e30a30f348afae7695d3bea12fef6","tid":132613,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5417f4de713e5d0246259a985d7d454eac640ff3","tid":132613,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太平紳士巡視, 高級監督巡視, 有無投訴</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以同太平紳士同倉?"},{"pid":"195ec3a802f3d76f837a253bdc0d3df1c20b79e4","tid":132613,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"